description: This common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 71, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 71, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Leverage for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [71 Votes, Common]
